name: CAPConcurrentInfections
title: CAP Concurrent Infections
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent concepts for concurrent infections for CAP patients.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element in the QDM category of Diagnosis.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts that describe infections that would be considered a risk factor for CAP patients if concurrently diagnosed with CAP.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
